<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="ideefc1fcc-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s1769"><num value="1769">§ 1769.</num><heading> “Agricultural commodity” defined</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The term “agricultural commodity” as used in this chapter includes any agricultural commodity or product thereof.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="ideefc1fcd-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/act/1954-08-28/ch1041">Aug. 28, 1954, ch. 1041</ref>, title VI, § 609, as added <ref href="/us/pl/95/501/tIV/s401/6">Pub. L. 95–501, title IV, § 401(6)</ref>, <date date="1978-10-21">Oct. 21, 1978</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/92/1691">92 Stat. 1691</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
